-= Kitchen =-
You find yourself in a kitchen. A standard kind of place. I guess you better just go and list everything you see here.

You make out an opened fridge. The fridge contains a fried pork chop and a block of cheese. You shudder, but continue examining the room. Were you looking for an oven? Because look over there, it's an oven. Suddenly, you bump your head on the ceiling, but it's not such a bad bump that it's going to prevent you from looking at objects and even things. You can see a table. On the table you see a cookbook. Huh, weird. You can see a counter. The counter is vast. On the counter you can make out a knife. Look over there! a stove. Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it. Hm. Oh well

There is an open frosted-glass door leading east. There is an exit to the south. Don't worry, there is no door.
